<tr>
<td>Microsoft .NET Framework 3.5 on Windows Developer Preview</td>
<td><a href="http://support.microsoft.com/kb/2633877" data-linktype="external">Microsoft Knowledge Base Article 2633877</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Microsoft .NET Framework 4.5 on Windows Developer Preview</td>
